title: Krypton
alt: Their Sun and gravity will make you, uh, something, I guess. Out of earshot from Earth, mostly.
transcript:
[Cueball and Megan are standing near a telescope.]
Cueball: The distant planet Krypton is becoming unstable!
Baby crying (from outside the panel): Waaaaaa
Megan: That crying baby is really annoying.[Cueball and Megan looking at each other.][Spaceship taking off.][Spaceship passing another spaceship on route to distant planet.][Planet exploding.]
